originalText.text: Sage Center Harlem is one of the nicest people that you ever wanted to meet the Staffing is very wonderful and also we have a good time there when I volunteer there I have wonderful experiences meeting some of the seniors talking to them and learning from the I thank God for going to this place it also helped me as a individual as a person to grow I recommend this place in any seniors that is lgbtq to come and visit there and any young people who wants to volunteer and to learn and to hear wonderful stories it activities to come are they always need help I will hope that the sage Center Harlem will always be there when I become a senior under the L G B T Q thank you so much love you Sage Center Harlem
